  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You point at a place within range, and conjure a glowing 1-foot ball of bubbling acid that streaks to the chosen location and explodes in a 15-foot radius sphere. Each creature in that area must make a Dexterity saving throw taking 10d4 Acid damage and 5d4 Acid damage at the end of its next turn and gains 1 rank of corrosion. On a successful save, a creature takes half the initial damage and suffer no further effects.</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above B-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and the initial damage by 2d4 and the lingering damage by 1d4.</p>",
